    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <p>The Vida Nueva weekend contains a series of talks given by a volunteer team of clergy, youth, and adults. The talks follow the basic themes of Christianity in its day-to-day application, and are followed by table discussions. Young men and women from age 15 to 20 may attend.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
